videos.headline: McClease takes it untouched for TD
videos.description: Hokies running back Deshawn McClease scores the first points of the game with a 4-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Hokies defense forces turnover
videos.description: Virginia Tech safety Terrell Edmunds intercepts Duke QB Daniel Jones and returns it 15 yards in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Jackson to Savoy for TD
videos.description: Virginia Tech QB Josh Jackson finds Sean Savoy for the 26-yard touchdown in the final seconds of the first half.

videos.headline: Jackson keeps it himself for TD
videos.description: Josh Jackson takes it in from 6 yards out to extend the Hokies lead in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Fuente proud of how team coped with elements
videos.description: Virginia Tech head coach Justin Fuente was proud of his team for having zero turnovers despite the torrential downpour.
